description:
Sponsored by the Toyota Crown Family.

On the second episode of Better Together, a series from Insider Studios in collaboration with the Toyota Crown Family, join leading marine conservationists from Happywhale and Oceans Initiative as they go on a whale-watching expedition in California. They use Happywhale’s AI platform to identify whales on the boat, then analyze their data on land working out of the generous cargo space of the Toyota Crown Signia.

Whatever your passion is, the Toyota Crown Family can help you get there. Learn more at https://www.toyota.com/toyotacrownfamily/ 

Learn more about Oceans Initiative at https://oceansinitiative.org/ 
Learn more about Happywhale at https://happywhale.com/home 

Missed the first episode of Better Together? Watch it here: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6jezePkXuWA
